OL,3,CPub-goers in Swindon being served
OL,4,Cshort measures, inspectors warn
OL,6,FPub-goers in Swindon are frequently
OL,7,Fbeing served short measures in some
OL,8,Fpubs and bars, a Trading Standards
OL,9,Fteam has warned.
OL,11,FIn a joint inspection with Swindon
OL,12,FBorough Council's Licensing
OL,13,Fdepartment, Trading Standards officers
OL,14,Fvisited 10 bars and pubs in the area.
OL,16,FThey found that over 70 per cent of
OL,17,Fthe drinks purchased were short
OL,18,Fmeasured.
