OL,3,CPub-goers in Swindon being served
OL,4,Cshort measures, inspectors warn
OL,6,FPosing as members of the public at
OL,7,Feach venue, Trading Standards officers
OL,8,Fordered a medium glass of white wine
OL,9,Fand a single vodka.
OL,11,FThe results of the survey found that
OL,12,F60 per cent of the glasses of wine
OL,13,Fbought were a short measure, while 80
OL,14,Fper cent of the vodka shots bought
OL,15,Fwere a short measure.
OL,17,FFor a medium glass of wine, the
OL,18,Fdeficiency was between 5ml and 25ml.
OL,19,FThe worst case was a 25ml deficiency
OL,20,Fon a 175ml glass of wine.
