OL,3,CPub-goers in Swindon being served
OL,4,Cshort measures, inspectors warn
OL,6,F"It is incumbent on all our pubs, bars
OL,7,Fand social clubs to ensure people are
OL,8,Fnot being short changed when they are
OL,9,Fspending their hard-earned money.
OL,11,F"Our Trading Standards team will
OL,12,Fcontinue to work with our licensed
OL,13,Fpremises to ensure they are serving
OL,14,Fthe correct measures as required by
OL,15,Flaw."
